  "character_name": "林路",
  "character_schedule": {
    "afternoon": "午睡被学院群消息吵醒——通知\"下周三前提交课程思政案例库材料\"，瞬间没了睡意。赶写课程思政案例，把《茅屋为秋风所破歌》和\"民生关怀\"结合，改了3遍才满意。",
    "day": 7,
    "evening": "刷B站，发现某些个历史博主在胡说八道，愤怒评论被拉黑，好生气。",
    "morning": "",
    "night": "",
    "noon": "坚持做黑暗料理，面条糊了，男学生来找他发现黑暗料理，有些不好意思。"
  },
  "comments": [],
  "completed": false,
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "content": "中午好啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "今天你也休息吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "对",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "你休息有什么安排吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "我要在家先美美睡到傍晚",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "然后再和闺蜜去逛吃逛吃",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "好啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "非常好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "我今天下午要工作",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "把思政案例材料交上去",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "嘿嘿，今天买了个特别漂亮的手链",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "什么样的？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "？水晶还是？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "黄金手链",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "今天是你生日吗？还是什么特殊日子？买大件了？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "不是啦，就一点点很小很小的黄金",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "也不是什么特殊日子，就想着最近上班太累了，给自己买一个黄金，奖励一下自己吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "而且不是保值吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "黄金首饰好啊，又能看还能收藏",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhh怎么说话这么人机啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "？你的赞美为何如此AI好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为我不大懂手势",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "无从下口",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "好吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "你还得再练练，再学学",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "和谁学？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "随机抽取不幸运的观众，让她啊陪我练习怎么鉴赏首饰？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "你觉得我怎么样？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "非常好，但是...",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "你愿意陪我练吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "为什么不愿意",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "？我是那么小气的人吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh那倒不是",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "但我对首饰的直男审美可能会让你不耐烦",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "到底有多直男？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "你喜欢粉色的东西吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "不是你想象中的那种觉得女生都应该喜欢粉色",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为我知道自己对女生的打扮没什么审美，所以我直接选简洁大方了的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "经典黑白灰",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "那也行",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "我年轻的时候就喜欢黑白灰，现在反而想要搞点bling bling的东西",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "你现在也很年轻啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "说的自己好像七老八十了一样",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "哎",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "我18岁的时候觉得自己年轻，真是无敌",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "18岁的我看着23岁的自己一定会觉得是个老人了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你该不会觉得27岁的我是个老头子吧？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯，没有老头这么夸张，但是有点老",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "[[sticker:uploads/upload_1771889220453290877.jpg]]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "你的话语好冰冷",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhhhhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "对了，你说金价还会涨吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "你问我吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "我包不靠谱啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "总之我觉得只要世界格局一天动荡，黄金就会持续的涨涨停停",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你觉得我要买更多的黄金吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "我觉得搞投资需要很强的承受能力",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "要是承受能力不强，投资赚的钱都不够出焦虑症的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "干嘛啊？好扫兴啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "啊？我就想手上有点闲钱存一点，在什么基金啊，黄金里",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "比我吃吃喝喝要强吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    }
  ],
